quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"By the chargers [horses ridden by warriors] panting"
  100,2,Then striking the sparks of fire
  100,3,Then raiding at dawn
  100,4,Then raising the dust therewith
  100,5,Then charging into the midst collectively therewith
  100,6,Man certainly indeed is ungrateful to his Lord
  100,7,And he certainly indeed bears witness on this (that he is ungrateful)
  100,8,And he is certainly indeed extremely fond of wealth
  100,9,Does he not know that when the contents of the graves are taken out and examined
  100,10,And that which was in (human) minds recovered
  100,11,"Their Lord shall have been well-aware of them, that Day"